description: Data was generated from file metadata from all studies information in the Cancer Imaging Archive (TCIA) from June 2017. http://www.cancerimagingarchive.net/#collections-list

fields.description: A unique collection name. Examples:TCGA-GBM, IvyGAP, QIN-HEADNECK, REMBRANDT, etc
fields.name: Collection

fields.description: Patient identifier- never blank. Examples:LIDC-IDRI-0908, LIDC-IDRI-0908
fields.name: PatientID

fields.description: Patient name for this study -- frequently the same as the PatientID, and sometimes left blank. Examples: 1.3.6.1.4.1.9328.50.4.076, 281949, QIBA_CT_1C
fields.name: PatientName

fields.description: The study date, of the form YYYY-MM-DD. Example: 1991-11-07
fields.name: StudyDate

fields.description: The number of series in this study. This is commonly between 1 and 5, but can be over 200.
fields.name: SeriesCount

fields.description: PatientSex is given as either M or F (may be left blank)
fields.name: PatientSex

fields.description: PatientAge is given in the format NNNY. Examples: 034Y, 111Y, 086Y(may be left blank)
fields.name: PatientAge

fields.description: Study Description. Examples: CT CHEST ABD PELVIS W/ CONTR, PET,HEAD & NECK CA RES
fields.name: StudyDescription
